Texts.Chs:
本指南将向您简要介绍如何正确的游玩Frackin'Universe。 您需要记住，屎大棒的许多成俗的游玩习惯已被MOD从许多方面所改变。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^yellow;三度仪 - 最好的朋友（迫真）:
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

本设备是任何时候^cyan;你物品中最有用的独特物品^reset;。 其提供对^orange;研究树系统的^reset;访问权限，除此之外你也可以通过其屏幕上的图标访问其他的许多功能。包括以下的功能:

^green;鼠标右键单击^reset; - 访问刃武跟踪器。您可以在其中访问FU教程并获得大量有用的奖励，建议花点时间在上面。

^green;Shift + 鼠标左键单击^reset; - 进入配置菜单。 通过此操作，您可以自定义物质枪的输出，甚至可以将自己选择工具交换到通常由画笔，电线工具等占据的格子中。非常方便。使用此功能，你可以把三度仪设置成永久性的热键项！


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;研究？研究是什么意思？能吃吗？^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

FrackinUniverse为游戏引入了全新的游戏进程大修，我们将其称作^orange;研究系统^reset;.。通过你的^orange;个人三度仪^reset;，^orange;SAIL计算机^reset;或者^orange;快捷栏^reset;访问 ，研究是您学习手工制作新蓝图的唯一方法。要解锁新蓝图，您将需要资源以及重要的货币^green;研究^reset;。

通过该系统，您将能够按照自己选择的顺序定制所需解锁的新科技。


只要您正在游戏，^green;研究^reset;就会以每2秒生产1点的速率产生。每级行星威胁等级此为速率增加+1。 因此，威胁等级6的行星将提供7点的总被动增益。

当然你也可以通过其他途径获得^green;研究^reset; ，包括 ^cyan;笔记本电脑和数据中心^reset;;
^cyan;化石收集^reset;
^cyan;显微镜^reset;
^cyan;持有巨量疯癫^reset;
^cyan;某些护甲和装备^reset;

简而言之，进行游戏和实验，您就能获得所需的所有研究。 ^red;注意：当您未进行探索时，研究效率会降低。^reset;.

如果您解锁了^red;应该^reset;显示在工作站上的东西，但似乎没有：确保^orange;已经升级^reset;了工作站。 创建更高级的物品仍然需要这像原版游戏那样。 


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^blue;
^cyan;种族能力^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

FrackinUniverse中的每个物种都有不同的游戏机制。有些人更耐火，而另一些人可能具有特殊的能力，或者是剑术大师。这为玩家提供了许多新的游戏选项。

^blue;译者温馨提醒：农神噬子，很不幸FR已被已经被FU吞噬，请取消订阅FR和其汉化，尤其是FR汉化，本汉化已并入其文本，未汉化的种族也在跟进，别抖机灵继续使用，以免造成不必要的笋湿，谢谢茄子。^blue;

^yellow;我不想整这些花活！^reset;

您可以在自己的^orange;飞船SAIL计算机^reset;处启用和禁用种族能力。只需访问它，按^green;[ MISC ] ^reset;按钮，然后选择禁用该选项。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;战斗^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
详见FU指南: 战斗


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;机甲^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
机甲与您在屎大棒原版中所惯用的不同。现在，它们需要^red;需要燃料^reset;，并且可以用许多类型的燃料为其加油。此外，耐久也从原版的耐久/燃料条中分离。 所以在FU中机甲是一辆更有用的载具，可以延长采矿行程，并大大提高在恶劣环境下的生存能力。

机甲现在会^green;计算他们的质量^reset;。^cyan;重型^reset;机甲可以对地面^green;践踏并造成伤害^reset; 且拥有更好的护甲。^cyan;轻型^reset;机甲^green;会快速很多^reset; 且极大的 ^green;提高燃料效率^reset;。

你的机甲可以双击^cyan;A^reset;或者^cyan;D^reset;^green;冲刺^reset;。

你的机甲可以双击^cyan;W^reset;切换至^green;飞行模式^reset;。

FU中增加了数十种新型的机甲零件，包括机甲模块。这些模块如同机甲版的EPP增强模块，并可以进行大量的自定义。机甲现在也是游戏风格的一部分。

通过^orange;个人三度仪^reset;可以为您的机甲加油或重新装配。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;状态影响^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
FrackinUniverse添加了^green;大量^reset;有益与有害的新状态效果，可以同时影响角色和怪物。多数的状态可以通过适当的装备抵抗或忽略。

经验的一部分是通过实验和聪明才智学习如何在新环境中生存，并制定策略围绕其^orange;研究^reset;。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;疯癫^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
FrackinUniverse中的另一种货币形式。 它可以从许多动作中获得（最常见的是见识不可名状之物），但随着时间的流逝也会逐渐消失。您拥有越多的^#e43774;疯癫^reset; ，您遭受的负面影响就越大。 在^green;研究^reset;中花费^#e43774;疯癫^reset;研究强大的^orange;玄学^reset;，^orange;心理顾问船员^reset;或者^orange;虚拟弗洛伊德^reset;机器都是在短时间内降低^#e43774;疯癫^reset; 的可靠方法。

随身携带的不详之物随着时间推移也可能导致^#e43774;疯癫^reset;。如果SAIL警告您，请留心。

^#e43774;疯癫^reset;有超过50种可能的影响。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;基因^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
这种货币取代了^red;33种独立的基因物品^reset;：这戏物品从2014年至2020年使用。现在，单独形式的^green;基因^reset;正式启用，可以让您更轻松地跟踪您的基因存量，并节约30多个存储资源。

^green;基因^reset;被用于^orange;农业^reset;和^orange;遗传学^reset;。

您只需将原来的基因放入基因提取器或植物分析台中，就可以将其换成新货币。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;BYOS (自定义飞船)^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
在FrackinUniverse中，您可以从头开始创建自己的飞船。 该系统意味着您不再需要购买“飞船升级”，因为任何扩展都是您自己完成的。您还需要制造自己的发动机，并且您还能制造特殊设备以使您的飞船受益。

请注意，如果在角色创建时选择BYOS模式，则此选择将会在该存档中永久生效。

在角色创建中，您可以选择^cyan;Frackin飞船reset;或^cyan;普通飞船^reset;。Frackin飞船就是选择BYOS的选项。选择后，将为您提供启动飞船配置的选项。而选择另外一项，就会像以前一样始游戏。

船员在这些船上使用特殊规则:

你可以使用^orange;船员合同^reset;，其与^orange;殖民合同^reset;遵循一样的规则(墙, 门, 光源, 床) ^red;

-或者-

^reset;如果你没有规划，习惯随地乱放，可以选择使用^orange;船员床^reset;。

您^red;不可以^reset;在同一房间里面同时使用^orange;船员合同^reset;合^orange;船员床^reset;。

BYO有12名工作人员的硬性上限。其他增加乘员限制的Mods可能无法在BYOS上正常运行。


BYOS船在建造方面还有其他选择，就是可以在冒险中证明有用的更好的发动机和推进器。

^red;救命，我的BYOS卡顿了！ ^reset; 或者 ^yellow;我不要在我的船上受大气影响^reset;!

BYOS的大气模式可以在^orange;飞船SAIL电脑^reset;.中启用和禁用。只需访问并找到^green;[ MISC ] ^reset;按钮，然后选择禁用该选项。


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;游泳^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
游泳的运作方式与您以前习惯的有所不同：

游泳 : ^yellow;W A S D^reset;

跳出水面 : ^green;按住^yellow;W^green;，再按^yellow;空格^reset;。

您可能需要一点时间来习惯它，但最终结果是更加轻松的控制体验。

请注意，并非所有液体都像水或其他类似液体一样提供浮力。在某些液体中或在气体中，物理行为可能与预期的完全不同。

Texts.Eng:
This guide will brief you on what you need to know to play with Frackin' Universe effectively. You need to keep in mind that a lot of the default play of Starbound has been altered by many aspects of the mod. 


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^yellow;The Tricorder - Your Best Friend:
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

This device is the ^cyan;singlemost useful item in your inventory^reset; at any time. It provices access to the ^orange;Research System^reset;, along with numerous other functions accessed via the icons on its screen. In also has the following additional functions:

^green;Right Mouse Button^reset; - Accesses the Quest tracker. This will provide you access to the FU tutorials and a wealth of useful rewards. It's well worth your time.

^green;Shift + Click^reset; - Accesses the Configuration menu. Through this you can customize your Matter Manipulator output, and can even swap your own chosen tools into slots normally occupied by the paintbrush, wire tool, etc. Very handy. Using this, you can make the Tricorder a permanent hotkey item!


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Research? What do you mean, Research?^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

FrackinUniverse now introduces a progression overhaul we've called the ^orange;Research System^reset;. Accessed through your ^orange;Personal Tricorder^reset;, ^orange;SAIL Computer^reset; or ^orange;Quickbar^reset; , it is the sole means by which you learn new blueprints for crafting. To unlock new blueprints you'll need resources as well as the important currency known as ^green;Research^reset;.

Through this system, you'll be able to custom-tailor the new unlocks you want and in the order you choose to pursue them.


You gain ^green;Research^reset; at a rate of 1 every second, passively, as long as you are playing. This rate increases by +1 per planet tier. Thus, a Threat 6 planet will provide 7 total passive gain.

You can also gain ^green;Research^reset; through other means, including: 
^cyan;Laptops and Data Centers^reset;
^cyan;Fossil Collection^reset;
^cyan;Microscopes^reset;
^cyan;Having high Madness^reset;
^cyan;Certain armor and gear^reset;

In short, play and experiment and you'll get all the research you need. ^red;NOTE: Research gain slows down while you are not exploring. AFK collection to easy-mode progression will not work.^reset;. 

If you have unlocked things that ^red;should^reset; appear at a station but do not seem to: Be sure you have ^orange;upgraded^reset; the station. That still needs to be done to create higher-tier items.

^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Racial Abilities^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;

Each of the various species in the FU universe has different gameplay mechanics. Some are more resistant to fire, while others might have special powers or are really good with swords. This provides players with many new gameplay options.

^yellow;I don't want to play with racial abilities^reset;!

You can enable and disable racial abilities from within your ^orange;ship SAIL computer^reset;. Simply access it, press the ^green;[ MISC ] ^reset;button and choose to disable the option.


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Combat^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
See FU Guide: Battle


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Mechs^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
Mechs are not the same as you're used to in Starbound. They now ^red;require fuel^reset;, and can be refueled with many types. In addition, they have separate Health from their Fuel/Energy bar. The end result is a much more useful vehicle that can extend mining trips and greatly improve survivability in harsh environments.

Mechs now ^green;calculate their Mass^reset;. ^cyan;Heavier^reset; mechs are able to ^green;stomp and do massive damage^reset; to the ground as well as having better armor. ^cyan;Light^reset; mechs are ^green;much faster^reset; and have vastly ^green;improved fuel efficiency^reset;.

Your mech can ^green;Sprint^reset; by double-tapping ^cyan;A^reset; or ^cyan;D^reset;.

Your mech can switch to ^green;Flight Mode^reset; by double-tapping ^cyan;W^reset;.

There are dozens of new types of mech part, including Mech Modules. These act like Augments for your Mech and can allow a great amount of customization. There's a mech part for your playstyle.

Refuel or Re-equip your mech through your ^orange;Personal Tricorder^reset;.


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Status Effects^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
FrackinUniverse adds a ^green;great number^reset; of new Status Effects, beneficial and harmful, that can affect characters and monsters alike. Most can be resisted or ignored with the proper equipment. 

Part of the experience is learning how to survive in new environments through experimentation and ingenuity, and strategizing your ^orange;Research^reset; around it. 


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Madness^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
Another form of currency in FrackinUniverse. It can be gained from many actions (most commonly the bizarre or terrifying) but will also fade away with time. The more ^#e43774;Madness^reset; you possess, the greater the negative effects you experience. Spending your ^#e43774;Madness^reset; through powerful ^green;Research^reset; in ^orange;Metaphysics^reset;, ^orange;Ship Counseller Crew^reset; or ^orange;Instafreud^reset; machines are all reliable ways to reduce ^#e43774;Madness^reset; in a hurry.

Carrying around terrifying things in your bag can also result in gaining ^#e43774;Madness^reset; over time. Pay attention if SAIL warns you of this.

There are more than 50 possible effects of ^#e43774;Madness^reset;.


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Genes^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
This currency replaced the ^red;33 separate Gene items^reset; used from 2014-2020. Now, a singular form of ^green;Gene^reset; is used, making tracking your totals much easier and giving you more than 30 less resources to store.

^green;Genes^reset; are used for ^orange;Agriculture^reset; and ^orange;Genetics^reset;.

You can trade in your current genes for the new currency by simply placing them into a Xeno Lab or Sprouting Table.


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;BYOS (Build your own Ship)^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
In FrackinUniverse, you can create your own ship from the ground up. This system means you no longer need to purchase Ship Upgrades, as any expansion is done by yourself. You'll also need to craft your own engines and will be able to craft special equipment to benefit your ship.
Note that if you select BYOS mode at character creation, this choice is permanent.

At Character Creation, you can select ^cyan;Frackin Ship^reset; or ^cyan;Vanilla Ship^reset;. The Frackin Ship is the BYOS option. Once you make this choice, you're given options for starting ship configurations. Once they make this choice, they begin play like usual.

Crew use special rules on these ships:

You can use ^orange;Crew Deeds^reset;, which follow the same rules as ^orange;Colony Deeds^reset; (Walls, Door, Lights, Bed) ^red;

-or-

^reset; you can opt to use ^orange;Crew Beds^reset; if quick-and-dirty with little planning is more your style. 

You can ^red;not^reset; use both a ^orange;Crew Deed^reset; and ^orange;Crew Bed^reset; together in the same room.

There is a hard-cap of 12 crew. Mods that increase crew limits likely will not operate properly with BYOS.

BYOS ships have additional options in construction, namely better engines and thrusters that can prove useful in exploration.



^red;'Help, I have BYOS lag!' ^reset; or  ^yellow;I don't want atmosphere effects on my ship^reset;!

BYOS has an atmosphere mode you can enable and disable from within your ^orange;ship SAIL computer^reset;. Simply access it, press the ^green;[ MISC ] ^reset;button and choose to disable the option.


^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
^cyan;Swimming^reset;
^blue;--------------------------------------------------^reset;
Swimming operates differently than you're used to:

Swim : ^yellow;W A S D^reset;

Jump Out : ^green;hold ^yellow;W^green; , press ^yellow;Spacebar^reset;. 

It will take you a bit to get used to it, but the end result is a much easier control experience.

Note that not all liquids provide buoyancy like water or other similar fluids. In these liquids, or within gases, physics can behave quite different than expected.
